<plot>The white folk of Jamaica are afraid that calypso music will replace "bop" (which in this film, is not a form of jazz, but describes rhythm &amp; blues and rock n' roll). A performance by mento master Lord Flea and his band shows that "calypso" is a formidable threat to "bop".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?079600</url></doc>
